{"tid":1472614,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈呼籲：示威者應該主動交出雷射槍，與警方交換其最抵武力橡膠槍等等","createTime":"2019-08-14T15:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T17:04:06.000Z","uid":62847,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dcbe327dcb91613af56f3dca814b49c3380913ea","tid":1472614,"uid":62847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"鑑於警方多次指責示威方使用高殺傷力的雷射槍與火魔法，造成暴力情況。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地應該展示友善一面，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主動請求警方交換武器</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n當示威一方使用催淚彈，橡膠子彈及布袋彈等，警方所認同既最低武力</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而警方使用高殺傷力既雷射槍。咁警方便不應有理由指責示威一方。畢竟，佢地使用既係 「公認的」最低武力。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁大隻夾乸，相信警方沒理由拒絕交換武器之約定。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母，垃圾警犬，天堂與地獄皆拒絕其入境申請。"},{"pid":"6b2e36468ca157215fbc3a1bcfd267f40071bb32","tid":1472614,"uid":62847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:29:32.000Z","msg":"誠邀警方與示威方 交換武器"},{"pid":"270ac9a687feda8161efd52cc27eb2451e3ff396","tid":1472614,"uid":108636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47430f4907cce7428a18860f4cf6edc34f0b24c","tid":1472614,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a457800b50997c436740495bdeaf37c12a97d46","tid":1472614,"uid":279995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"1d38cd7690cf14f9bbf240f7b51f4ce23bbb26bc","tid":1472614,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\